{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"body":"Gerrit #879 patchset 1 CI exposed collateral .pytest_cache creation by nested pytest in clean runners. Fixed the oracle helper to pass -p no:cacheprovider, preserving the nested behavioral run while preventing checkout mutation. Focused 45 passed and make check passed after correction; amended commit cc255012cdaacc054598eab8852c8d1bcfea75dd pushed as patchset 2 with the same Change-Id."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1784694924049100001,"uuid":"33ee6bd2-f3a8-411d-b710-e6205fd12720"}